unittitle_ssm: United Automobile Workers of America, Local 2110 Records
abstract_ssm: The Technical, Office and Professional (TOP) Union, Local 2110, is an amalgamated union with over 30 contracts covering workers in universities, publishing, museums, law firms and other offices. They represent teachers, secretaries, administrators, editors, computer operators, librarians, museum curators, typesetters and graphic artists, and other workers. The records of UAW 2110, 1942-2004 consist of contracts and agreements between organizations and their employees, pamphlets and brochures, correspondence including emails, shop files, reports, financial material, archived websites, and VHS tapes.
